Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請輸入名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.51,0:00:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根津公彥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人為什麼能掩藏著生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說畏懼現實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.89,0:00:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人害怕真實的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從很久以前就被四周的人討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不過是按自己所想的去生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.97,0:01:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一肯和這樣的我坦然接觸的人，只有幸田真志了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他卻是我最恨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨完全和我不同的他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開朗 比誰都可愛 我恨他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那溫暖的家庭中長大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他對我的態度完全沒有差別待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像把他的優越感隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想對他復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓要奪走所有他所珍惜的東西，他所愛的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自私是你的所有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全照著你所想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笨蛋先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1話 我是如何踏出第一步的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要向真志告白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想這樣放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不說清楚是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是真志是不會把我當普通朋友以外的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的話，能夠做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕就和你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝，美裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個傢伙戴著假面具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐島美裡，還是高橋加南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美裡和加南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都喜歡，都不想傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一個都不想傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡這麼軟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經有了計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡真志嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想將真志據為己有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你一把也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說出真話了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實真志也很重視你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果好好跟他告白的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心加南嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶她一起去 告白的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真志會選擇你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說清楚對朋友也是一種善意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（這樣一來，她們會為了真志互相背棄朋友）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心臟快爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫他來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加南
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公彥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真志是不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真志君 喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加南
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美裡，這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誤會？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不、那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，我知道加南的心意\N可是不想就這樣放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:09:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且加南也會困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想為了她而犧牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊，不要為了我犧牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說誰都不想傷害是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復仇的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美裡心裡早就計算好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以加南的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不會有所反抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 加南的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還隱藏著未被開發出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加南 明知有人偷窺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還故意留著縫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加南內心想被人看的慾望，我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想對加南做些事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:11:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是對真志的復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有別的人可以拜託了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真志有事忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐島她利用了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把真志據為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她為了把真志據為己有不惜犧牲你這個摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你像個笨蛋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把車停下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊很難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催淫劑，提起你的性慾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，快別忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公彥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事，這車從外面看不到裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對，無需忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服就別忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的東西要來就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣，感覺到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來，再來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己就先去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我好好堅持到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你背叛朋友的證據（網聊記錄）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被揭穿就麻煩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威脅?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不累嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政治上活躍的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,興趣是公益的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被這些無聊的光環困住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用盡全力去做個名門的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊 你想要的東西一定要弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼樣的手段都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的本性，暴露的話，你就完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濕了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:17:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 大小姐這麼敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強姦犯的樣子照下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以強姦罪逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕什麼的我才不信，你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我是同一種人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:18:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要焦急 我們之間的關係才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快，把我脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這麼開，不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濕的一塌糊塗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在裡面動得好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吧
